data.description: 3.625% Assumable VA Loan, good for the debt on the loan, great opportunity for lower rates! This charming 2-story gem, nestled in the fantastic Crowfield neighborhood, boasts 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and a versatile FROG/4th Bedroom. Embrace the potential of this cozy haven, perfect for family living.  The main level invites you into a warm and spacious living area, perfect for creating lasting memories around the wood burning fireplace. The kitchen, though functional, awaits your personal touch for modern upgrades. Upstairs, discover three comfortable bedrooms, with the master featuring an ensuite bath for your private retreat.  Unwind in the FROG, a flexible space ready to adapt to your lifestyle - be it a home office, gym, or an extra bedroom. The expansive backyard provides a paver pati& fire pit area plus a canvas for your dream outdoor oasis. Enjoy the convenience and camaraderie of a welcoming neighborhood with great amenities such as Golf Course, Hiking Trails, Tennis Courts, Swimming Pools & Community Parks, while being just moments away from great amenities and schools. This home is priced with your budget in mind, allowing room for updates and personalization. Don't miss the chance to turn this house into your dream home - a place where memories are made and futures unfold. Your vision, your home - come see what 120 W Hartwick can do for you!
